      "writtenOn": "2018-05-24T19:10:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The first two are needed because we actually allocate more bytes than sizeof(SkAtlasTextBlob)\nto store arrays.\n\nI tried to delete the last one, but this seems needed to make placement new work in ::Make.",
