        "id": 5085
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-05-24T19:23:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Builds fine for me with all of these removed. I\u0027m not sure what the first two are protecting us from as this isn\u0027t subclassed (could be final) and has no public constructors.",
      "parentUuid": "6640b77e_c693cce1",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 107,
        "startChar": 0,
